WEBVTT

1
00:32:12.307 --> 00:32:16.103 
原来之前你是多么失败  多么愚蠢
What a sucker you've been. What a fool.

2
00:32:16.395 --> 00:32:19.064 
答案就在那儿  始终未曾远离
The answer was there all the time.

3
00:32:19.314 --> 00:32:23.819 
这一切的起因  只是个小小的意外
It took a small accident to make it happen.

4
00:32:24.736 --> 00:32:27.406 
-一个意外  -一个意外
- An accident! - An accident!

5
00:32:27.656 --> 00:32:30.200 
我就这么发现了那个秘密
That's how I discovered the secret.

6
00:32:30.826 --> 00:32:33.787 
那种  难以捉摸的元素
That elusive ingredient.

7
00:32:34.037 --> 00:32:36.498 
那道火花
That spark...

8
00:32:36.748 --> 00:32:39.793 
那是生命的吐息
...that is the breath of life.

